Property.Name: QueryScript
Property.Value: SELECT dbo.Applications.Id AS AppId, dbo.ApplicationTypes.Name AS AppTypeName, dbo.SubmittedDocuments.Id AS SubmittedDocId, dbo.SubmittedDocuments.DocType, dbo.SubmittedDocuments.DocName, dbo.Applications.SubmittedDate, dbo.Applications.Status FROM dbo.Applications INNER JOIN dbo.SubmittedDocuments ON dbo.Applications.Id = dbo.SubmittedDocuments.Id INNER JOIN dbo.ApplicationTypes ON dbo.Applications.Id = dbo.ApplicationTypes.Id

Property.Name: HeaderContents
Property.Value: CREATE VIEW dbo.vAppDoc AS

Property.Name: QueryScript
Property.Value: SELECT dbo.Applications.Id AS AppId, dbo.ApplicationTypes.Id AS AppTypeId, dbo.AspNetUsers.Id AS AspNetUserId, dbo.ApplicationHistories.Id AS AppHistoryId, dbo.ApplicationHistories.ApplicationId FROM dbo.Applications INNER JOIN dbo.ApplicationHistories ON dbo.Applications.Id = dbo.ApplicationHistories.ApplicationId INNER JOIN dbo.ApplicationTypes ON dbo.Applications.ApplicationTypeId = dbo.ApplicationTypes.Id INNER JOIN dbo.AspNetUsers ON dbo.ApplicationHistories.TriggeredBy = dbo.AspNetUsers.Id

Property.Name: HeaderContents
Property.Value: CREATE VIEW dbo.vAppHistory AS

Property.Name: QueryScript
Property.Value: SELECT dbo.Applications.Id, dbo.ApplicationTypes.Id AS AppId, dbo.ApplicationTypes.Name AS ApplicationName, dbo.Inspections.Id AS InspectionId, dbo.Inspections.InspectionDocument, dbo.SubmittedDocuments.Id AS SubmittedDocId, dbo.SubmittedDocuments.DocName, dbo.SubmittedDocuments.DocType, dbo.AppFees.ApplicationFee, dbo.FacilityTypes.Name AS FacilityTypeName FROM dbo.AppFees INNER JOIN dbo.ApplicationTypes ON dbo.AppFees.ApplicationTypeId = dbo.ApplicationTypes.Id INNER JOIN dbo.Applications ON dbo.ApplicationTypes.Id = dbo.Applications.ApplicationTypeId INNER JOIN dbo.FacilityTypes ON dbo.AppFees.FacilityTypeId = dbo.FacilityTypes.Id INNER JOIN dbo.Inspections ON dbo.Applications.ApplicationTypeId = dbo.Inspections.ApplicationId INNER JOIN dbo.SubmittedDocuments ON dbo.Applications.Id = dbo.SubmittedDocuments.ApplicationId

Property.Name: HeaderContents
Property.Value: CREATE VIEW dbo.vApplication AS

Property.Name: QueryScript
Property.Value: SELECT dbo.Countries.Id AS CountryId, dbo.Countries.Name AS CountryName, dbo.States.Id AS StateId, dbo.States.Name AS StateName, dbo.LGAs.Id AS LGAId, dbo.LGAs.Name AS LGA_Name, dbo.Companies.Id AS CompanyId, dbo.Companies.Name AS CompanyName FROM dbo.States INNER JOIN dbo.Companies ON dbo.States.Id = dbo.Companies.StateId INNER JOIN dbo.Countries ON dbo.Companies.CountryId = dbo.Countries.Id INNER JOIN dbo.LGAs ON dbo.States.Id = dbo.LGAs.StateId

Property.Name: HeaderContents
Property.Value: CREATE VIEW dbo.vCountries AS

Property.Name: QueryScript
Property.Value: SELECT dbo.Facilities.Name, dbo.Facilities.Address, dbo.Facilities.IsLicensed, dbo.FacilityTypes.Name AS FacilityTypeName, dbo.Companies.Name AS ComapnyName, dbo.Tanks.Name AS TankName, dbo.Tanks.Capacity, dbo.Facilities.Id, dbo.Companies.Id AS CompanyId, dbo.Tanks.Id AS TanksId, dbo.Products.Id AS ProductId, dbo.Products.Name AS ProductName, dbo.FacilityTypes.Id AS Expr5 FROM dbo.Products INNER JOIN dbo.FacilityTypes INNER JOIN dbo.Tanks INNER JOIN dbo.Facilities ON dbo.Tanks.FacilityId = dbo.Facilities.Id INNER JOIN dbo.Companies ON dbo.Facilities.CompanyId = dbo.Companies.Id ON dbo.FacilityTypes.Id = dbo.Facilities.FacilityTypeId ON dbo.Products.Id = dbo.Tanks.ProductId

Property.Name: HeaderContents
Property.Value: CREATE VIEW dbo.vFacilities AS

Property.Name: QueryScript
Property.Value: SELECT dbo.ApplicationTypes.Id AS AppTypeId, dbo.ApplicationTypes.Name AS AppTypeName, dbo.FacilityTypeDocuments.Id AS FacilityTypeDocId, dbo.FacilityTypeDocuments.DocumentTypeId AS DocTypeId, dbo.FacilityTypeDocuments.DocType, dbo.FacilityTypeDocuments.Name AS DocName, dbo.FacilityTypeDocuments.IsFADDoc FROM dbo.FacilityTypeDocuments INNER JOIN dbo.ApplicationTypes ON dbo.FacilityTypeDocuments.ApplicationTypeId = dbo.ApplicationTypes.Id

Property.Name: HeaderContents
Property.Value: CREATE VIEW dbo.vFacilityDoc AS

Property.Name: QueryScript
Property.Value: SELECT dbo.ExtraPayments.Id, dbo.Payments.ExtraPaymentId FROM dbo.Payments INNER JOIN dbo.ExtraPayments ON dbo.Payments.ExtraPaymentId = dbo.ExtraPayments.Id

Property.Name: HeaderContents
Property.Value: CREATE VIEW dbo.vPayments AS

Property.Name: QueryScript
Property.Value: SELECT dbo.Permits.ApplicationId AS AppId, dbo.Applications.FacilityId, dbo.Facilities.Name AS FacilityName, dbo.Permits.Id AS PermitId, dbo.Permits.PermitNo, dbo.Permits.IssuedDate AS IssueDate, dbo.Permits.ExpireDate AS ExpiredDate, dbo.Facilities.IsLicensed AS Licensed FROM dbo.Permits INNER JOIN dbo.Applications ON dbo.Permits.ApplicationId = dbo.Applications.Id INNER JOIN dbo.Facilities ON dbo.Applications.FacilityId = dbo.Facilities.Id
